        -:  252:     *     → retry dequeue from own queue (then neighbours)
        -:  253:     *
        -:  254:     * Using a single condvar (not per-thread) keeps the producer fast: one
        -:  255:     * unconditional mutex_lock/signal/unlock per enqueue, regardless of how
